685
00:49:33,840 --> 00:49:36,434
ls that right? Tell me you're
not seriously entertaining this.

686
00:49:36,560 --> 00:49:39,120
Vince, this is
a drastic situation we got.

687
00:49:39,240 --> 00:49:42,550
-Those are our men up there!
